title: Siddharta Concert DVD (Bezigrad stadion 2003) unofficial
description:
Full concert DVD preformed on Ljubljana stadion with Simphony orcestra and 40 dancers in front of 35.000+ people.

Songs : Japan, T.H.O.R., Rooskie, Rave, Et Tu, Rain, Siddharta, Klinik, My Dice, Eboran, Pot v X, Samo Edini, Neon, Na Soncu, Kloner, B Mashina, Od Visine se zvrti, Keltvek, Orion Lady, Etna, Under Venus, Insane, Apokalipsa

A MUST SEE FOR ALL ROCK FANS !!
